	<a name="footnote46-00785_002_039">46.</a>
      </span>
				<p class=""><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.57-59?lang=spa#56" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 138:57–59</a>; V&eacute;ase tambi&eacute;n <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.30-34?lang=spa#29" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 138:30–34</a>.</p>
